    {cmd:invnchi2(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:np}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)}
{p2colset 8 22 22 2}{...}
{p2col: 描述：}逆累积非中心卡方分布：如果
	{cmd:nchi2(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:np}{cmd:,}x{cmd:)} = {it:p}，则
	{cmd:invnchi2(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:np}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)} = {it:x}{p_end}
{p2col: 范围 {it:df}:}2e-10 到 1e+6 （可能非整数）{p_end}
{p2col: 范围 {it:np}:}0 到 10,000{p_end}
{p2col: 范围 {it:p}:}0 到 1{p_end}
{p2col: 值域：}0 到 8e+307{p_end}
{p2colreset}{...}